 Burna Boy Popular musician streaming site, BoomPlay has released its official figures for the most streamed male musicians from Sub-Saharan Africa. The list which is dominated by Nigerian musicians saw award-winning Nigerian musician, Burna Boy being the most streamed musician. The first three in the list is completed by his compatriots Fireboy DML and Joeboy. This will make Burna have all the bragging rights over his greatest nemesis, Davido and his new friend, Wizkid.